# Beplus Fast Product Filter & Live Search for WooCommerce ŌĆö plugin blocks

Standards: [`Document Plugin.md`](../../Document Plugin.md) ┬¦ Gutenberg Blocks. Skills: `bpss-add-plugin-block`.

## Registration and build

- One folder per block under `blocks/` with `block.json`.
- `BlockRegistry` auto-discovers via `register_block_type_from_metadata()`.
- Built assets via wp-scripts ŌåÆ `build/blocks/` (or block-local `index.js` + `index.asset.php` if using custom pipeline).
- Extension filter: `beplus_fast_product_filter_live_search.blocks`.

## block.json conventions

- `textdomain`: `beplus-fast-product-filter-live-search-for-woocommerce`
- `category`: `beplus-fast-product-filter-live-search-for-woocommerce`
- `name`: `beplus-fast-product-filter-live-search-for-woocommerce/{slug}` (e.g. `beplus-fast-product-filter-live-search-for-woocommerce/search-bar`)
- Prefer `render: file:./render.php` for dynamic search UI.
- Attributes: camelCase (`placeholder`, `showIcon`, `maxResults`, `enableLiveSearch`).

